title: Lance Wells from Faded Grey
itunes:title: Lance Wells from Faded Grey
description:
I am pleased to bring you this great chat with my friend Lance Wells who is the vocalist of Las Vegas hardcore band Faded Grey. If you have never listened to them, rectify that immediately. We get in deep with skating as a gateway, desert life and the Army of Kids. Lance opened up a lot and I was very happy to have this conversation. Enjoy! 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
